    "description": "We at Ipca Laboratories Ventures Solutions are looking for an experienced Surgeon based out of Ahmedabad. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Ipca Laboratories Ventures Solutions:\nIpca Laboratories Ventures Solutions is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Collaborate with pharmaceutical representatives and medical suppliers\n• Participate in quality improvement initiatives and clinical audits\n• Educate patients and families on health management and disease prevention\n• Monitor patient progress and adjust treatment plans accordingly\n• Administer medications and treatments as prescribed\n• Provide high-quality patient care and maintain patient records\n• Respond to medical emergencies and provide immediate care\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Master's degree preferred\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Medical Coding\n• Proficiency in Telemedicine\n• Proficiency in Health Informatics\n• Proficiency in HIPAA Compliance\n• Proficiency in Surgical Procedures\n• Proficiency in Infection Control\n• Proficiency in Medical Terminology\n• Proficiency in EMR/EHR\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Flexible working hours\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ahmedabad, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Ipca Laboratories Ventures Solutions!",
